check trucks and goods through the border.
</P>
<P>
Some transportation firms and individuals are still trying to
smuggle goods into Mozambique to dodge tariffs, he said.
</P>
<P>
The last truck detention took place on March 3.
</P>
<P>
Following the tightened check at the Ressano Garcia checkpoint
by Mozambique, goods carried into the southern African country
have reduced sharply, local reports said.
</P>
<P>
The South African police have taken the corresponding
measures, said the reports.
</P>
<P>
