<TEXT>
<P>
RABAT, March 15 (Xinhua) -- Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak
said here today that the Al-Qods (Jerusalem) Committee of the
Organization of Islamic Conference will hold a session within 10
days to discuss the Israeli plan to build new housing in East
Jerusalem.
</P>
<P>
The Al-Qods Committee will express its indignation over the
Israeli plan which goes in contrary to the spirit of Oslo
agreements signed between Israel and Palestinians, said Mubarak at
