Mubarak ruled out the possibility of calling for an Arab summit
to discuss Israel's new housing plan in Jerusalem, saying that the
Al-Qods Committee is the proper forum to debate this question.
</P>
<P>
Mubarak, who arrived here from the United States on Friday, had
held talks with King Hassan II on the situation of the Middle East
peace process and the meeting of Al-Qods Committee, of which
Morocco is presently the president, said Moroccan officials.
