<HEADLINE> Netherlands Beat Australia, England Ties Pakistan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISALABAD, March 16 (Xinhua) -- Olympic champions the
Netherlands beat Australia 3-2 while the reigning world champions
Pakistan were held 1-1 by England on the opening day of the
five-nation hockey tournament in Karachi, on Sunday.
