<HEADLINE> International Meeting on Anthropology Opens in Nepal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, March 16 (Xinhua) -- An international conference
opened here today to discuss ways to make anthropological and
sociological studies more effective in the future.
</P>
<P>
The four-day conference on anthropology and sociology,
organized by Nepal's Tribhuvan University and a local institute,
is scheduled to review and analyze the activities being carried
out in the fields in the Asia and Pacific region, identify
existing problems and work out a common work policy.
</P>
<P>
