crisis has been created intentionally to import electricity from
India.
</P>
<P>
She also criticized the government for extending transit to
India while keeping the nation in total darkness about it.
</P>
<P>
"The government has entered into a more stringent agreement
with India. It would jeopardize the future of the nation and make
it the target of insurgency from across the border," she warned.
